Package: ubigen
Title: Graphical Interface for Finding Ubiquitous Genes
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(
        "Elias",
        "Projahn",
        email = "elias@johrpan.de",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4153-4071")
    )
Description: This package contains precomputed data including comparisons in
    gene expression. It provides a graphical interface to analyze and visualize
    those data to rank genes based on how ubiquitously expressed they are.
